cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.GR 

The paper focuses on generative adversarial networks (GANs) for image creation and modification, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The addition of an encoder network also brings in elements of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of the Capsule Network as a discriminator is a novel technique in image processing (cs.NE) and graphics (cs.GR).
